<br>
You can leave his PH alone and kill the rest, but the PH will aggro, so you have to feign him off over and over if you don't want to kill him and risk spawning the rogue. <br>
<br>
Kurosh gives no faction, btw. <br>
<br>
I would have to say though that the only reason to ever bother working of Brood of Kotiz is if you have to do a quest, like Greenmist for my Ogre for instance. I see no reason whatsoever for a monk to raise it, unless you're just a faction junkie. It's even more tedious than the bone chips, imho, and the payoff is insignificant.<br>
<br>
There are only 4 times you will ever run into a necro Iksar to my knowledge.  <br>
<br>
Grype - In the Tink n Babble. He only spawns at night and there is no reason to even go past his building.<br>
<br>
Hermit - Right next to Lake of Ill Omen zone.  Unless you blunder down into his hallway, he'll never aggro on you as you go to the zone.<br>
<br>
Firiona Vie - I don't know this guys name. I haven't played a good race since pre-kunark, but it's the guy who spawns at the river/ocean place that slays all the newbies. Easily avoided.<br>
<br>
Necro tower in W Cabilis - Only a completely oblivious person could accidentally wander within aggro range of this gigantic structure that has necros standing outside in robes. You can easily go around the building, on either side and use the vendors, exit the zone, etc.  If you die here, it's cause you were very, very careless. <br>
<br>
I say pass on the Brood of Kotiz unless you just want to take screenshots of yourself hanging out in with the necro trainers.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ujibjabhonorbound.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jibjab Honorbound</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_thatch.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 38<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/16/02 5:36:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32034.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.sc.rr.com/honorbound/images/monkey_brains.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Field of Bone</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Firiona Vie - I don't know this guys name. I haven't played a good race since pre-kunark, but it's the guy who spawns at the river/ocean place that slays all the newbies. Easily avoided.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->If this is Vekis you're refering to, who spawns next to the Iksar Statue, she's not on Necro faction. I think she's on Trooper faction, since she /cons warmly to me, and I'm still KOS to necros.<br>
